query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mk t mc) NoMergeJoin(mc mk t mi) */ select count(*)
from movie_keyword AS mk
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND mk.keyword_id = 398 AND t.production_year > 1950 AND t.production_year < 2000
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.company_type_id = 2
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id;
